{"id":232937086,"title":"前車違規閃避而自摔，請益🙇🏻‍♀️","content":"前幾天剛起步速度不快，已經過了路口為了閃避一台違規迴轉的貨車而自摔，附上簡圖如下\n（手傷簡單畫，請見諒！）\n藍色是貨車\n綠色是我的機車\n箭頭是行車方向\n綠色叉叉是我摔車地點\n路口當時是綠燈號誌\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/f62d8ecc-8afd-4a8c-bdce-f0cae3f376e6/1280.jpeg\n事發當下貨車車主有靠邊停下叫警察\n警察來後才幫忙叫了救護車\n做完筆錄後警察沒詢問是否和解\n事過兩天打電話給對方\n對方老闆主張沒碰撞\n不願私下和解 堅持要貨車的保險公司理賠\n且要我自費去做鑑定\n\n聽了實在很美宋 \n要過年了 我因為對方違規而受傷\n而對方無論車還是人皆整株好好\n對方態度還很惡劣\n想準備資料齊全先提過失傷害 \n請問各位這樣合理嗎？\n還有能否請大家建議其他處理方式","excerpt":"前幾天剛起步速度不快，已經過了路口為了閃避一台違規迴轉的貨車而自摔，附上簡圖如下，（手傷簡單畫，請見諒！），藍色是貨車，綠色是我的機車，箭頭是行車方向，綠色叉叉是我摔車地點，路口當時是綠燈號誌，事發當","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"d208d1e2-6f14-429b-97b7-75a2dd4f761c","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-22T06:59:33.377Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-22T07:36:17.766Z","commentCount":9,"likeCount":9,"tags":[],"topics":["車禍"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"汽機車","forumAlias":"vehicle","school":"中國文化大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":9}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/f62d8ecc-8afd-4a8c-bdce-f0cae3f376e6/1280.jpeg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"6b9ea91f-1d56-4522-8333-f667f648bf74","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/f62d8ecc-8afd-4a8c-bdce-f0cae3f376e6/640.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/f62d8ecc-8afd-4a8c-bdce-f0cae3f376e6/640.jpeg","thumbnail":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/f62d8ecc-8afd-4a8c-bdce-f0cae3f376e6/640.jpeg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-22T06:59:33.377Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-22T07:36:17.766Z","width":296,"height":640},{"id":"6b9ea91f-1d56-4522-8333-f667f648bf74","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/f62d8ecc-8afd-4a8c-bdce-f0cae3f376